			</p>

			<div class='cta-div'>
				<a
					href='{{verificationUrl}}'
					target='_blank'
					class='btn btn-primary block center'
				>Forgot your password?</a>
			</div>

			<p class='text'>
				If you have a questions or need any assistance, feel free to reach out
				to our support team at
				<span class='purple-text'>app@gmail.com</span>
			</p>

			<p class='salutation text'>
				<span class='block'>Best regards,</span>
				<span class='block purple-text'>node-api-boilerplate</span>
			</p>

		</div>
		<div class='footer'>
			<div class='footer-main'>
				<div class='container'>
					<strong class='text'>
						Did you receive this email by mistake or have any questions?
					</strong>
					<p class='text'>
						You can contact the sender by clicking the button below
					</p>
					<a href='#' class='btn btn-secondary block center'>Contact Us</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class='text grey-text invite-info'>This invite will expire in 1 hour</p>
		</div>
